---
[v1] arm64: dts: mediatek: add soc phandle label

Add 'soc' phandle label to the soc node in mt7988a device tree to allow
other nodes to reference it using &soc syntax.
---
v1: Move openwrt-master files to openwrt-25.12 branch after OpenWrt official
    25.12 branch release.
---

--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a.dtsi
@@ -184,7 +184,7 @@
 		};
 	};
 
-	soc {
+	soc: soc {
 		compatible = "simple-bus";
 		ranges;
 		#address-cells = <2>;
